rows.label: qev035703_MSG0002
rows.name:
Our team has been traveling Mira.
We crush their camps as we find them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035703_MSG0003
rows.name:
It is satisfying work. Like fighting for freedom.
Far better feeling than before.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035703_MSG0004
rows.name:
You must help Captain Slovity.
She puts up cheery front. But it is lie.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035703_MSG0005
rows.name: Inside, she rages at Ganglion for hurting us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035703_MSG0006
rows.name:
At times, rage consumes her. Makes her careless.
That may give our enemies opening.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035703_MSG0007
rows.name:
I cannot stop her once her mind is set. But you can.
You must keep level head. Keep her safe.[ST:wait ]
